structure.unit: DIVISION OF INSURANCE AND INSURANCE GENERALLY (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Created 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 105, sec. 12, effective June 17, 1948.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Examination, by director, of rating organizations, advisory organizations, and joint underwriting or joint reinsurance organizations; report of examination; public inspection.
